description: Lists all of the import jobs.

nested_items.name: ImportJobs
nested_items.description: A list of the import job summaries.

nested_items.name: JobId
nested_items.description: A string that represents a job ID.

nested_items.name: ImportDestination
nested_items.description: An object that contains details about the resource destination the import job is going to target.

nested_items.name: SuppressionListDestination
nested_items.description: An object that contains the action of the import job towards suppression list.

nested_items.name: SuppressionListImportAction
nested_items.description: The type of action to perform on the address. The following are possible values:
PUT: add the addresses to the suppression list. If the record already exists, it will override it with the new value.
DELETE: remove the addresses from the suppression list.

nested_items.name: ContactListDestination
nested_items.description: An object that contains the action of the import job towards a contact list.

nested_items.name: ContactListName
nested_items.description: The name of the contact list.

nested_items.name: ContactListImportAction
nested_items.description: >The type of action to perform on the addresses. The following are the possible values:
PUT: add the addresses to the contact list. If the record already exists, it will override it with the new value.
DELETE: remove the addresses from the contact list.

nested_items.name: JobStatus
nested_items.description: The status of a job.
CREATED --- Job has just been created.
PROCESSING --- Job is processing.
ERROR --- An error occurred during processing.
COMPLETED --- Job has completed processing successfully.

nested_items.name: CreatedTimestamp
nested_items.description: The date and time when the import job was created.

nested_items.name: ProcessedRecordsCount
nested_items.description: The current number of records processed.

nested_items.name: FailedRecordsCount
nested_items.description: The number of records that failed processing because of invalid input or other reasons.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: A string token indicating that there might be additional import jobs available to be listed. Copy this token to a subsequent call to ListImportJobs with the same parameters to retrieve the next page of import jobs.
